{"tid":1289126,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"［歐聯黑氣石］保方：同C朗並肩係一份禮物","createTime":"2019-07-06T03:06:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T03:59:02.000Z","uid":43785,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"90467ed9f60306d923b6c7c6cf030359ccf5e8b2","tid":1289126,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T03:06:08.000Z","msg":"保方：同C朗並肩係一份禮物<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5N48wic.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5N48wic.jpg&h=0217aa7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now Sports-體育】意大利門神保方直言能夠與基斯坦奴朗拿度並肩作戰，是祖雲達斯贈予他的一份禮物。<br />\n<br />\n「與基斯坦奴朗拿度合作實在好，我在去季有機會與冠軍級的尼馬與基利安麥巴比共事，現在，感謝祖雲達斯，我將有機會與朗拿度合作。這是一份美好的禮物。」保方（Gianluigi Buffon）回巢後少不免被問及對C朗的看法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n41歲的他上季由祖雲達斯加盟巴黎聖日耳門，原意是衝擊未曾贏過的歐聯，結果未能如願，合共出賽25場後宣佈離隊，預計他回歸後難重奪正選，而是出任施捷斯尼的副手。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這位於2001年從帕爾馬加盟祖雲達斯的門將，合共在意大利聯賽上陣640場，只要多賽8場就可打破馬甸尼的意甲出賽紀錄。完成本季後，他該會擔任球會管理層工作。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n較早前，他已表明會改穿77號波衫，為此他再作補充：「這代表我的歷史，我在帕爾馬時用過這號碼，那予我好運。我實在很喜歡。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n祖記今年都唔使旨意攞歐聯了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"